p: The HA gene of this virus was similar to that of the H2N3 strain isolated in Mongolia (2015), whereas the NA gene of our isolate was similar to that of the H10N9 strain isolated in Bangladesh (2010). The viral genes PB2 and PA were 98.9% and 99.49% identical to the PB2 and PA genes of A/duck/Jiangsu/SE0261/2018 (H5N3).
